{"tid":1183782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"六四隨時係香港發生 有圖有真相","createTime":"2019-06-03T07:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T08:00:24.000Z","uid":241444,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48b5b78b2d551838734de54171d67beeabb69c81","tid":1183782,"uid":241444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"利申90後 唔好話咩政治冷感<br />\n六四係中國人死關我咩事？<br />\n個陣未回歸都可能唔關你事，<br />\n依加香港比番大陸一國兩制名全實忘，<br />\n老實講聽前人講六四咩坦克咩鎮壓，<br />\n冇經歷冇見過確實冇咩感覺，睇完圖再講！<br />\n<br />\n有圖慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.aboluowang.com/2015/0607/567669.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.aboluowang.com%2F2015%2F0607%2F567669.html&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=c97409c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.aboluowang.com/2015/0607/567669.html</a><br />\n<br />\n本身仲諗50年內搵方法慢慢走，<br />\n如有逃犯條例真係之後有咁快走咁快<br />\n但點撚解我明明係香港人咁逃離香港啊<br />\n就算走某外國唔係最好，都好撚過依加個香港啊<br />\n屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月9號上街！冇咩望都好可能係最後一次！<br />\n到時莫須有你唔好搵人求救<br />\n<br />\nSor for 19999"},{"pid":"2f10dccc6068428f6d97b0c0bc2406c50547ede9","tid":1183782,"uid":241444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"Sor for 開錯台"},{"pid":"c95aa84b3efd225b81bef42de65d23315955b9d1","tid":1183782,"uid":187565,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"名<span style=\"color: red;\">存</span>實<span style=\"color: red;\">亡</span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbb8d4d44c23f811296e4437a96fabbf78f9dcd","tid":1183782,"uid":241444,"like":1,"dislike":4,